description: [First posted in AWOL 29 March 2012, updated 26 November 2013]. Çatalhöyük Databases On-line. This area of the website gives you direct access to the excavation and other specialist data as recorded during the excavation season. We will be updating the data available periodically but if there is any particular data you would like to see please to see if we can help. There are two ways to explore our excavation data. You can either browse the available data which offers you categories of information to look at to help guide you through our datasets, or if you have a more specific query in mind you can choose from our variety of.
title: Çatalhöyük Databases On-line
